## Problem
Native HTML checkboxes are used in poll creation form. They have no neo-brutalist styling and labels are barely visible in dark mode.

## Files
- Create: `frontend/src/lib/components/ui/Checkbox.svelte`
- Modify: `frontend/src/lib/components/ui/index.ts` (add export)
- Modify: `frontend/src/routes/(dashboard)/polls/new/+page.svelte`
- Modify: `frontend/src/routes/(dashboard)/booking-links/new/+page.svelte` (if checkboxes exist)

## Implementation
Create a styled checkbox component:
```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  interface Props {
    checked?: boolean;
    label?: string;
    description?: string;
    disabled?: boolean;
    onchange?: (checked: boolean) => void;
  }
  let { checked = $bindable(false), label, description, disabled = false, onchange }: Props = $props();
</script>

<label class="checkbox-wrapper">
  <input 
    type="checkbox" 
    bind:checked 
    {disabled}
    onchange={() => onchange?.(checked)}
    class="checkbox"
  />
  {#if label}
    <span class="label">{label}</span>
  {/if}
</label>

<style>
  .checkbox-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .checkbox {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    cursor: pointer;
    appearance: none;
    display: grid;
    place-content: center;
  }

  .checkbox:checked {
    background: var(--sky);
    border-color: var(--sky);
  }

  .checkbox:checked::before {
    content: '';
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: white;
    clip-path: polygon(14% 44%, 0 65%, 50% 100%, 100% 16%, 80% 0%, 43% 62%);
  }

  .checkbox:focus {
    outline: 2px solid var(--sky);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .label {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
```

## Verification
- Navigate to polls/new
- Checkboxes should have neo-brutalist styling
- Labels should be readable in dark mode
- Checked state should show sky blue background with white checkmark
